# linux-temp-admin release signing public key (ed25519, hex-encoded, 64 hex chars).
#
# CONFIGURED: signed self-upgrade is ENABLED. `upgrade` verifies each downloaded
# release binary against this key before installing it, failing closed on any
# mismatch. The matching PRIVATE key is held OFFLINE by the maintainer (generated
# via `go run ./cmd/lta-release keygen`); only scripts/release.sh uses it.
#
